Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.98,0:00:10.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,3004)}So Ra No Wo To
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.20,0:01:47.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.94,0:01:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Advance!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.90,0:01:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Advancing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.23,0:01:57.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Enemy sighted.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.74,0:01:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare to fire main cannon!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.01,0:02:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Distance 800.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.75,0:02:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gunner, load HE round!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.60,0:02:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.57,0:02:06.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Loading complete!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.06,0:02:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Prepare to fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.62,0:02:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Fire!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.78,0:02:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boom!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.53,0:02:22.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Target hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.44,0:02:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Signal the\Nforces to our rear.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.30,0:02:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One enemy unit destroyed.\NFollow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.12,0:02:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.43,0:02:39.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One enemy unit destroyed, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.59,0:02:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice work!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.00,0:02:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're not there yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.77,0:02:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Filicia, it's Claus!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.20,0:02:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My... Then let's have tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.60,0:02:52.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.38,0:03:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mountain Hiking\N- The Ends of the World
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.59,0:03:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shuko's doing a lot better!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.38,0:03:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her wound has healed,\Nbut she's stayed here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.00,0:03:14.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this place is wonderful, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.35,0:03:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.32,0:03:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How can she be that\Nactive in this heat?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.06,0:03:26.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.86,0:03:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is from HQ.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.30,0:03:31.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I need your signature here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.96,0:03:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.00,0:03:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And here are some letters\Nand packages for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.40,0:03:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kana-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.90,0:03:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.08,0:03:44.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Yes! Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.76,0:03:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.44,0:03:50.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.23,0:04:01.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's from my mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.85,0:04:03.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And for you, too, Noël.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.69,0:04:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From your beloved Professor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.87,0:04:07.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Professor?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.37,0:04:08.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.16,0:04:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His family name is Pro.\NHis given name is Fessor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.33,0:04:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're very common\Nnames in Sept.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.70,0:04:18.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Fessor, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.56,0:04:21.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's wonderful that you have\Nfriends from so far away!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.14,0:04:24.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.62,0:04:27.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.13,0:04:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on, Noël.\NI believed you for a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.70,0:04:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take Claus a present.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.36,0:04:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.17,0:04:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.26,0:04:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.21,0:04:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Throw it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.01,0:05:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what did HQ say?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.99,0:05:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.83,0:05:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Kureha?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.03,0:05:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Major Claus... Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.93,0:05:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This year's, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.89,0:05:48.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.40,0:05:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,U-Uh, th-thank you\Nfor everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.96,0:05:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.99,0:05:56.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.21,0:06:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Major.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.72,0:06:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.94,0:06:23.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.90,0:06:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll take care of the place\Nwhile you're gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.26,0:06:25.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.39,0:06:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good luck out there, Private.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.20,0:06:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.94,0:06:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, we're going on\Na field trip tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.85,0:06:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.54,0:06:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A field trip, she said!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.74,0:06:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that great, Noël-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.48,0:06:41.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you psyched?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.67,0:06:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A field trip... Filicia?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.06,0:06:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just walking would be boring,\Nso we're going to have a game, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.23,0:06:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Game?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.49,0:06:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You all know that there are\Nold-era observation devices
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.02,0:06:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,placed on the south side of Seize.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.14,0:07:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, the border between\Nus and no man's land.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.00,0:07:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three of them are up for their\Nregular maintenance check.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.00,0:07:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like you to look at them\Nall on your trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.35,0:07:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.56,0:07:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a mission!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.62,0:07:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's just a field trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.29,0:07:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if they're broken,\Nwe can't do anything about them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.32,0:07:25.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noctur-type observation devices\Nare a complete black box.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.72,0:07:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible to disassemble them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.26,0:07:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's a field trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.80,0:07:33.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is what he meant by\N"Good luck out there."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.32,0:07:35.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But just walking isn't\Ngood enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.49,0:07:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thus...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.70,0:07:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be carrying those!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.18,0:07:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're feeble.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.28,0:07:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, the way to carry these is by\Nputting your weight forward...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.43,0:08:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.68,0:08:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... I can't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.56,0:08:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Screw up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.55,0:08:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like you're one to talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.80,0:08:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really are such good children.\NYou did exactly what we thought you would!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.85,0:08:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Argh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.26,0:08:22.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen! When carrying\Na heavy pack,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.10,0:08:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,first, you lean back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.21,0:08:26.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.13,0:08:32.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once the weight of the pack\Nis completely on your back...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.97,0:08:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pathetic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.23,0:08:48.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop talking...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.41,0:08:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.71,0:08:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.93,0:08:58.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK! Then Filicia and I
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.35,0:09:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,will proceed straight to the goal point\Non the map to wait for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.53,0:09:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you really think you can't\Ngo on, blow your trumpet.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.94,0:09:08.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll come to look for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.57,0:09:10.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.01,0:09:13.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And there are wild animals\Non this mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.76,0:09:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Should you encounter one,\NI'll leave it up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.99,0:09:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have permission to use\Nyour weapons if necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.14,0:09:19.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.32,0:09:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK, guys. Have fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.23,0:09:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Face right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.23,0:09:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Face right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.45,0:09:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Advance forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.15,0:09:38.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Advance!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.96,0:09:53.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.59,0:09:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK, the rest is up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.12,0:09:59.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.68,0:10:05.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heavy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.04,0:10:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heavy! Heavy, heavy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.33,0:10:13.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha-chan, don't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.58,0:10:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The more you say that,\Nthe heavier it gets.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.37,0:10:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noël, how much farther?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.40,0:10:23.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noël!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.30,0:10:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kanata!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.86,0:10:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Found it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.30,0:10:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.62,0:10:58.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.28,0:11:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Functioning normally. No issues.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.37,0:11:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.42,0:11:16.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We found that one easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.52,0:11:18.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's keep it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.90,0:11:19.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.70,0:11:25.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.16,0:11:27.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, just...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.51,0:11:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just thinking, it's been protecting\Nthe town, all alone, this whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.19,0:11:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, Noël,\Nwhere's the next one?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.72,0:11:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.16,0:11:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're here now, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.66,0:11:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.72,0:12:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Th-That mountain?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.50,0:12:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone do something\Nabout these bags!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.98,0:12:46.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heavy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.61,0:12:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it. The captain and\NRio-sempai both hate me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.89,0:12:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.17,0:12:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why they're doing this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.87,0:12:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heavy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.20,0:13:02.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, say something, Kanata!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.63,0:13:06.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like you not\Nto say anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.96,0:13:09.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.80,0:13:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.18,0:13:13.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.12,0:13:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can hear you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.10,0:13:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can hear you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.34,0:13:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.09,0:13:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kanata!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.20,0:13:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.00,0:13:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's broken?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.40,0:13:40.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.47,0:13:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so cool down here!\NAnd so pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.01,0:13:58.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Break time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.44,0:14:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care what anyone\Nsays. It's break time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.47,0:14:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.04,0:14:06.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First in!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.90,0:14:08.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.87,0:14:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is good!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.60,0:14:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get you for that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.66,0:14:24.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.94,0:14:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just for the heck of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.64,0:14:37.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noël, you...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.31,0:14:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.90,0:14:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kureha-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.40,0:14:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, this is fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.01,0:14:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.09,0:14:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's not!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.03,0:14:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not taking this\Nseriously enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.24,0:14:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a field trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.32,0:14:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to enjoy it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.65,0:15:00.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you forget about\Nthose ten-ton sacks?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.19,0:15:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is training!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.45,0:15:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Filicia-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.34,0:15:07.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get a clue already!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.05,0:15:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.73,0:15:10.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The devil herself!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.07,0:15:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But she's got blonde hair\Nand her skin is so pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.02,0:15:17.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't mean anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.80,0:15:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kureha doesn't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.35,0:15:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Understand what?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.54,0:15:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what's good about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.50,0:15:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.23,0:15:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.65,0:15:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys must know\Nsome other Filicia!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.32,0:15:32.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez! Someone do something\Nabout these goody-two-shoes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.95,0:15:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time for food! Hooray for food!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.13,0:15:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're soaked...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.10,0:15:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll dry quick in this sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.54,0:15:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.48,0:15:53.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our food's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.62,0:15:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was it a boar maybe?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.92,0:15:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.86,0:16:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the countryside back home,\Nthey tear up fields all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.34,0:16:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's a lot of food for them in the summer,\Nso you normally don't see them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.19,0:16:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a bigger problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.07,0:16:08.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.38,0:16:09.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The compass is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.71,0:16:10.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.19,0:16:17.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if it was OK\Nto leave those bags.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.83,0:16:21.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've gotta focus on reaching\Nthe goal now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.77,0:16:23.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are we going the right direction?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.99,0:16:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The first device was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.35,0:16:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.25,0:16:32.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're on the mountain with the\Nsecond device at its summit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.64,0:16:35.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we just need to head upward.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.70,0:16:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,OK! We'll get there,\Nno matter what-
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.40,0:16:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hungry, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.29,0:16:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if there's anything\Nwe can eat...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.12,0:16:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.75,0:16:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bayberries!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.38,0:16:57.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you eat them?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.17,0:16:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.83,0:17:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're sweet and a little\Nsour. They're good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.02,0:17:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The sounds made a chord!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.69,0:17:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we can't get up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.75,0:17:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.75,0:17:10.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.07,0:17:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.27,0:17:16.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They say Major Claus once\Ncrossed a desert in a tank,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.11,0:17:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for three days and nights, with no food,\Nto take out an enemy fortress!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.70,0:17:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.22,0:17:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.36,0:17:24.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've never heard that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.84,0:17:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They call him the Desert Wolf.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.82,0:17:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.23,0:17:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow... Claus-san is?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.89,0:17:34.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's do our best!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.31,0:17:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But the bayberries...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.17,0:17:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No whining!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.90,0:17:49.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Found number two!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.50,0:18:06.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A boar?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.77,0:18:21.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the last one?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.19,0:18:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's getting pretty dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.22,0:18:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So we'll have to keep\Nchecking our direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.35,0:18:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this really the right way?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.14,0:18:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.96,0:18:34.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, "Probably"?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.04,0:18:37.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't be one hundred percent\Nsure without a compass.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.41,0:18:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then what? We've come\Nall this way for nothing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.31,0:18:43.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I'm saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.22,0:18:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the compass is that important,\Nyou should've kept it with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.40,0:18:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.87,0:18:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's not fight here, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.42,0:18:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your fault for playing\Nin the river.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.45,0:18:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.15,0:18:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.29,0:18:59.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not taking this seriously!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.68,0:19:01.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you mean, field trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.39,0:19:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're such an airhead,\Nsmiling like an idiot all the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.79,0:19:07.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we're in this mess!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.04,0:19:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you understand that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.28,0:19:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.05,0:19:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.84,0:19:21.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.35,0:19:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.96,0:19:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.68,0:19:30.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sheesh... I guess they'll be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.25,0:20:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Goal!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.95,0:20:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.32,0:20:12.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it, Kureha-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.12,0:20:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it, I get it, so get off me!\NI can't breathe...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.30,0:20:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.71,0:20:37.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No Man's Land.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.14,0:20:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the end of the inhabited world.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.23,0:20:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good work!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.71,0:20:55.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Captain, I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.41,0:20:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't complete our mission!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.49,0:21:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What mission?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.40,0:21:02.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.70,0:21:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, it's a field trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.69,0:21:06.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.43,0:21:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We just wanted you to see this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.69,0:21:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These are the signatures of\Nthose who came before us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.43,0:21:19.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the fortress maidens came\Nhere at least once.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.53,0:21:25.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And they saw this...\NThe end of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.69,0:21:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is history, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.71,0:21:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sure is... Can you\Nwalk a bit more?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.81,0:21:41.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's one more thing\Nthey've left us.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.45,0:21:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're late!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.69,0:22:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rio-sempai?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.63,0:22:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.51,0:22:07.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.55,0:22:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bayberries!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.46,0:22:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel alive again.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.22,0:22:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, did you win?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.89,0:22:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.31,0:22:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it was worth the effort...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.93,0:24:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Kanata's Day Off - Hair Braiding
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.57,0:24:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.85,0:24:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kanata's Day Off.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.26,0:24:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hair Braiding.
